title: Aliens Ate My Babysitter Remix
content:
After a few weeks of messing around with Fruity Loops, and producing some bad Commander Keen songs, I have decided to take on my biggest challenge yet - a remix. I chose Aliens ate my babysitter because... no one did it yet (I think).

Anyway, I always thought of what Keen would find floating out in space with his Photachyon Transceiver so I decided to base it off of that idea. Here is the link.

Link is dead, sorry.

I tried to stay away from anything that would make it too ambient or noisy. I hope you enjoy it. If you don't.... eh whatever [img]http://www.classicgaming.com/cc314/msgboard/emotikeen-crazy.gif[/img] .-----------------------
Save a little money each month and at the end of the year you'll be surprised at how little you have.
